-- reverse-string-crystal.cell: string reversal crystallization
-- LLM reverses a string, then crystallize proposes вҠў= form

вҠў reverse
  given text вүЎ "hello world"
  yield reversed

  вҲҙ Reverse the characters in В«textВ».
    "hello" вҶ’ "olleh"

  вҠЁ reversed = "dlrow olleh"

вҠў crystallize
  given В§reverse
  given reverseвҶ’reversed
  yield В§reverse', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§reverseВ». It reverses a string character by character.
    Write a вҠў= expression that does the same thing.
    Return the crystallized cell and whether the transformation is faithful.

вҠў verify-crystal
  given В§reverse'
  given crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful
  given reverseвҶ’reversed
  yield approved

  вҲҙ Does В«В§reverse'В» produce "dlrow olleh" for input "hello world"?
    Compare against the original output В«reverseвҶ’reversedВ».

  вҠЁ if approved and crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful then В§reverse' may replace В§reverse
